The Encompas Mental Health Wellness Program provides confidential, customized and safe mental health support and services. The Program is powered by Dalton Associates – a third party Mental Health Organization. No participant information is shared with either the Employer or the Association.     

Supports include 24/7/365 access to concierge wrap-around Care Management who will facilitate streamlined and expedited access to vetted and occupationally aware mental health services and resources.   

Services include: 24/7/365 crisis support, counselling support, psychological assessments, psychiatric consultations, residential and intensive outpatient treatment programs, lifetime aftercare support, and a Member Portal with access to progress measurement tools and exclusive vetted mental wellness resources.
